{"tid":1462930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一路都唔明有班人話去機場目的係向旅客宣傳","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T12:23:27.000Z","uid":28068,"like":44,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"50b3d1366de5a839b86f6e019eeb5bd1c65e2340","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"主要目的由頭到尾都係癱瘓機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打擊香港經濟，攬炒先係重中之重<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始變左向旅客宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宣傳俾遊客呢d根本係極之次要<br />\n講真你作為遊客呢段時間黎香港就預左交通會好大阻塞<br />\n<br />\n所以請回歸重點係癱瘓機場<br />\n唔係乜9向旅客宣傳"},{"pid":"5a72ab2a394904662695a410858d53f8dbbec9e3","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:42:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e7befaa5091f608a68007c603821af81aa8431","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:42:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1451ebb73f01436b3f7850b7c87fca9a7cd8201","tid":1462930,"uid":61105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"一開始個陣係為左宣傳（之前一連三日個個），之後我地人多左，個目標就進取左變左癱瘓"},{"pid":"7daa398dfb0a8ed30ed29916f3f2476b7760d78d","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9da8d0ee2f41eb374e8984e2057b7ebd178fbe9e","tid":1462930,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:47:09.000Z","msg":"借post:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 談社運正當性 ] 塞鐵阻人返工可以係因為依個香港佢地有份；亦解釋到點解唔好塞離境旅客~</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1462734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1462734</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿我唔係講策略/效果既問題。<br />\n<br />\n無疑塞鐵/罷工會惹人反感，唔應該日日做。<br />\n<br />\n但亦無可否認既，就係依類不合作運動係有佢既道德正當性係入面，因為返工既人多數都係香港社會既一份子，而佢地係有責任去維護香港人既人權自由；所以你阻佢，就算對社運進程無好處都好，你都係出師有名。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相對地，離境旅客有好多都唔係香港既持份者，基本上佢地係無任何責任為我地既人權自由付出任何代價；最簡單既理解方法，就係我相信你自己都唔會認為自己對其他國家既人權自由有絕對既責任，反之亦然。<br />\n<br />\n所以，離境旅客係搞不得。<br />\n<br />\n但，我地有權去機場、有權係唔阻其他旅客既情況下坐地下，所以靠人多去令機場function唔到，責任就唔係我地度，剛剛星期一既塞爆機場亦係絕對無問題。"},{"pid":"ca37893449a65aeec021f3113a2862dc1d6b5fcd","tid":1462930,"uid":64273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"叫下面啲人上departure"},{"pid":"293ba042b346278ba3bfe7b27627ef540e25ea52","tid":1462930,"uid":108269,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:47:35.000Z","msg":"走都走唔到，點宣傳？"},{"pid":"a117e2251a462ec6730b57a3d688edf608739c09","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b1451ebb73f01436b3f7850b7c87fca9a7cd8201","tid":1462930,"uid":61105,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"一開始個陣係為左宣傳（之前一連三日個個），之後我地人多左，個目標就進取左變左癱瘓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"我都有去<br />\n講真所謂既宣傳真係吃力不討好<br />\n有睇下新聞都知咩事<br />\n洗乜咁晒大家力氣黎嗌口號"},{"pid":"9f879506ff8e03f35501cd412e24d5adabbb7993","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db77d7281c02905c2bfd109ec272f924f4edb901","tid":1462930,"uid":33053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02aa2812a7335f8ef545a4abc22690b30df0f88","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd9edda9ce44dd5cfcb938e3fea6bc94e633960","tid":1462930,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:49:30.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"5c93ae3b60d6d6ae3730fab5279abe0dc9cec07b","tid":1462930,"uid":61105,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"q